public interface Versioned
    Provides an abstraction of a plug-and-play component in conjunction with the Mastered and Iterated interfaces. The intent is that in a business model an object would assert that it is a version by inheriting the Versioned interface. With this assertion the business object can then be revised and copied to new versions. In order to create a new Versioned object REVISE access is required.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
    See Also:
    VersionControlHelper, VersionControlHelper.service, AccessPermission.REVISE
